      <title>比特币期权需求不断增长：Cboe 的 Hocking</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-02/demand-growing-for-bitcoin-options-cboe-s-hocking-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[CBOE Global Markets Inc. 推出首个与比特币现货价格相关的现金结算指数期权，标志着传统交易所最新增加了加密货币相关证券。CBOE Global Markets 产品创新主管 Rob Hocking 与 Eric Balchunas 和 Scarlet Fu 谈论了此次发布。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-02/demand-growing-for-bitcoin-options-cboe-s-hocking-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 19:09:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
